law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 496, sec. 62, effective July 1, 1999. -- Amended 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 371, sec. 9, effective July 15, 1996. -- Created 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 512, sec. 55, effective July 15, 1994.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Use of approved modified rating methodology required for issuance or renewal of plans -- Geographic rating areas -- Exemption -- Permitted deviation from index community rates.
